quotes: Rules are made to be broken... like buildings! Or people!
You've never had to survive in this world.
You're not the only one who's had a hard life.
They all abandoned me, but not you.
I'll show them they were wrong.
It's always more fun when it explodes.
You want to play? Then, let's play!
Nobody understands me, except my toys.
We're going to have so much fun!
